@startuml
actor User
participant Frontend
participant Backend
database DB

User -> Frontend: Sceglie un servizio e data/ora
Frontend -> Backend: POST /Backend/v1/bookings {service_id, scheduled_at, notes}
Backend -> DB: Valida service_id, crea booking
Backend -> DB: Inserisce pagamento con prezzo del servizio
DB --> Backend: Booking e Payment creati
Backend --> Frontend: 201 Created { booking }
Frontend -> User: Mostra conferma prenotazione
@enduml